      • create

        public static SlideShow<?,?> create(java.io.InputStream inp)
                             throws java.io.IOException,
                                    EncryptedDocumentException
        Creates the appropriate HSLFSlideShow / XSLFSlideShow from the given InputStream.

        Your input stream MUST either support mark/reset, or be wrapped as a BufferedInputStream! Note that using an InputStream has a higher memory footprint than using a File.

        Note that in order to properly release resources the SlideShow should be closed after use. Note also that loading from an InputStream requires more memory than loading from a File, so prefer create(File) where possible.

        (从给定的InputStream创建适当的HSLFSlideShow /XLLFSlideShow。您的输入流必须支持标记/重置，或者包装为BufferedInputStream！请注意，使用InputStream比使用File具有更高的内存占用空间。请注意，为了正确释放资源，SlideShow应在使用后关闭。另请注意，从InputStream加载比从File加载需要更多内存，因此尽可能首选创建（File）。)
        Parameters:
        inp - The InputStream to read data from.(inp -用于读取数据的InputStream。)
        Returns:
        The created SlideShow(创建的SlideShow)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if an error occurs while reading the data(java.io. IOResponse-如果读取数据时发生错误)
        EncryptedDocumentException - If the SlideShow given is password protected(加密文档异常-如果给出的SlideShow受密码保护)

      • create

        public static SlideShow<?,?> create(java.io.InputStream inp,
                                    java.lang.String password)
                             throws java.io.IOException,
                                    EncryptedDocumentException
        Creates the appropriate HSLFSlideShow / XSLFSlideShow from the given InputStream, which may be password protected.

        Your input stream MUST either support mark/reset, or be wrapped as a BufferedInputStream! Note that using an InputStream has a higher memory footprint than using a File.

        Note that in order to properly release resources the SlideShow should be closed after use. Note also that loading from an InputStream requires more memory than loading from a File, so prefer create(File) where possible.

        (从给定的InputStream（可能受密码保护）创建适当的HSLFSlideShow /XLLFSlideShow。您的输入流必须支持标记/重置，或者包装为BufferedInputStream！请注意，使用InputStream比使用File具有更高的内存占用空间。请注意，为了正确释放资源，SlideShow应在使用后关闭。另请注意，从InputStream加载比从File加载需要更多内存，因此尽可能首选创建（File）。)
        Parameters:
        inp - The InputStream to read data from.(inp -用于读取数据的InputStream。)
        password - The password that should be used or null if no password is necessary.(密码-应该使用的密码，如果不需要密码，则为空。)
        Returns:
        The created SlideShow(创建的SlideShow)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if an error occurs while reading the data(java.io. IOResponse-如果读取数据时发生错误)
        EncryptedDocumentException - If the wrong password is given for a protected file(CryptedDocument异常-如果为受保护的文件提供了错误的密码)

        public static SlideShow<?,?> create(java.io.File file,
                                    java.lang.String password,
                                    boolean readOnly)
                             throws java.io.IOException,
                                    EncryptedDocumentException
        Creates the appropriate HSLFSlideShow / XSLFSlideShow from the given File, which must exist and be readable, and may be password protected

        Note that in order to properly release resources the SlideShow should be closed after use.

        (从给定的文件创建适当的HSLFSlideShow /XLFSlideShow，该文件必须存在且可读，并且可能受到密码保护。请注意，为了正确释放资源，SlideShow在使用后应关闭。)
        Parameters:
        file - The file to read data from.(文件-要从中读取数据的文件。)
        password - The password that should be used or null if no password is necessary.(密码-应该使用的密码，如果不需要密码，则为空。)
        readOnly - If the SlideShow should be opened in read-only mode to avoid writing back changes when the document is closed.(只读-如果SlideShow应以只读模式打开，以避免在文档关闭时写回更改。)
        Returns:
        The created SlideShow(创建的SlideShow)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if an error occurs while reading the data(java.io. IOResponse-如果读取数据时发生错误)
        EncryptedDocumentException - If the wrong password is given for a protected file(CryptedDocument异常-如果为受保护的文件提供了错误的密码)
